  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/29a82d325ee3ca2d2a0bdfd228b57f9e.avif?t=1749385147\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/e18aaadc42710a08ec61447b4fed786a.poster.avif?t=1749385147\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/e18aaadc42710a08ec61447b4fed786a.webm?t=1749385147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/1a2d2597b9157248bbee137ae68fc2be.avif?t=1749385147\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saya is a yuki-onna, a type of snow demon, living a peaceful, but lonely life on the Eastern continent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her world is turned on its head when she's kidnapped by slavers who intend to sell her on the distant Western continent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She escapes the slavers, but finds herself stranded in a strange foreign land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She resolves to return to her home, but earning the money to book passage back to the East will bring her into conflict with humans and monsters of all sorts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Saya make it home, or does fate have something else in store?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leveling System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantasy Setting</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/29a82d325ee3ca2d2a0bdfd228b57f9e.avif?t=1749385147\" width=620 height=76 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/e18aaadc42710a08ec61447b4fed786a.poster.avif?t=1749385147\" width=620 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/e18aaadc42710a08ec61447b4fed786a.webm?t=1749385147\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1585540/extras/1a2d2597b9157248bbee137ae68fc2be.avif?t=1749385147\" width=620 height=474 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saya is a yuki-onna, a type of snow demon, living a peaceful, but lonely life on the Eastern continent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her world is turned on its head when she's kidnapped by slavers who intend to sell her on the distant Western continent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She escapes the slavers, but finds herself stranded in a strange foreign land. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She resolves to return to her home, but earning the money to book passage back to the East will bring her into conflict with humans and monsters of all sorts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Saya make it home, or does fate have something else in store?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG Experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based Combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leveling System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill System</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantasy Setting</p></li></ul>",
